Logout
public class Logout
extends AbstractMethod

This method logs a session out.

Subsequent API calls using the logged out SessionID will result in errors.

Version:
1.2.0
Author:
Riyad Kalla

execute

public Logout.LogoutResponse execute(String url,
                                     String apiKey,
                                     String sessionID)
Convenience method used to execute the smugmug.logout method.

This method performs necessary conversions on all the argument values before calling execute(String, String[]).

Parameters:
url - The URL of the SmugMug server to communicate with. Either secure or unsecured URLs are fine to use for this method.
apiKey - The API Key to use. API keys are issued by SmugMug.
sessionID - The logged in SessionID that represents the user's session that will be logged out.
Returns:
the response that occurs from logging the user off.
